        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Frequent, high potency healing keeps the team sustained.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Can adapt to the situation by choosing offensive or defensive buffs.\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Very powerful ultimates can turn the tide of battle with relative ease.\n\n",
          "bold": false,
          "color": "white"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Weaknesses\n",
          "bold": true,
